───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Original Author: Claude (Anthropic)
Project: WinMerge AI Review Exporter
Version: 1.1.0

This project was created as an internal development tool to help developers
export and analyze code diffs from WinMerge for architecture reviews using LLMs.

Key Features:
  - Multi-mode redaction (FULL, API-Safe, SIGNATURE)
  - Risk scoring for changed files
  - Token estimation and cost analysis
  - Pure-Python diff generation (no external tools required)
  - GUI and CLI interfaces
  - Stripped Patch mode with selective identifier pseudonymization

Development History:
  - v1.0.0: Initial release with basic diff export and risk scoring
  - v1.0.1: Fixed pyproject.toml build backend, added pure-Python folder compare
  - v1.1.0: Added API-Safe redaction mode, full English UI, improved CLI

